result.name: Invasion Process of Fall Armyworm in the Eastern Hemisphere
result.description: This investigation delves into the genetic evolutionary of 124 specimens of fall armyworm, sourced from 14 locales across both the Western and Eastern Hemispheres. By reconstructing the migration trajectories, we elucidate the invasion pathway of the species into the Eastern Hemisphere.
result.center: College of Plant Protection, Yunnan Agricultural University
